description: Deployment & infra rules for DevOpsAgent
alwaysApply: true
---

- Build images with **Cloud Build** (Dockerfile at repo root).
- Images stored in **Artifact Registry** (`us-central1-docker.pkg.dev/project/ai-team/*`).
- Deploy via **Cloud Run** revisions, traffic 100 % to new rev only after `/healthz` returns 200 three times.
- DB migrations run inside a Cloud Build step using `alembic upgrade head`.
- Rollback strategy: `gcloud run services update --revision` to previous stable rev.
